    {
      "id": "FBNyuvHeaNXvaB_ZF7V1l",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 970.3691900344129,
      "y": 2864.1113433837886,
      "width": 379.3797607421875,
      "height": 225,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0O",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 504069395,
      "version": 6,
      "versionNonce": 348432407,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1783519612183,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. Classic Search\nint l = 0, r = n - 1;\nwhile (l <= r) {\n    int mid = l + (r - l) / 2;\n    if (nums[mid] == target) return mid;\n    if (nums[mid] < target) l = mid + 1;\n    else r = mid - 1;\n}\nreturn -1;",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. Classic Search\nint l = 0, r = n - 1;\nwhile (l <= r) {\n    int mid = l + (r - l) / 2;\n    if (nums[mid] == target) return mid;\n    if (nums[mid] < target) l = mid + 1;\n    else r = mid - 1;\n}\nreturn -1;",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "oatjSLLFrUItIIw5W23Ky",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 965.3691900344129,
      "y": 3114.111343383789,
      "width": 406.63629150390625,
      "height": 250,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0Q",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1131767613,
      "version": 13,
      "versionNonce": 88787161,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1783519612183,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "2. Lower Bound (First Position ≥ Target)\nint l = 0, r = nums.length;\nwhile (l < r) {\n    int mid = l + (r - l) / 2;\n    if (nums[mid] < target)\n        l = mid + 1;\n    else\n        r = mid;\n}\nreturn l;",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "2. Lower Bound (First Position ≥ Target)\nint l = 0, r = nums.length;\nwhile (l < r) {\n    int mid = l + (r - l) / 2;\n    if (nums[mid] < target)\n        l = mid + 1;\n    else\n        r = mid;\n}\nreturn l;",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "l-Woj7qGVrCHibEesMOff",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 962.0358567010796,
      "y": 3395.7780100504556,
      "width": 408.57977294921875,
      "height": 275,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0T",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 29582643,
      "version": 121,
      "versionNonce": 1615170871,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1783519612183,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "3. Binary Search on Answer\nint l = minPossible, r = maxPossible;\n\nwhile (l < r) {\n    int mid = l + (r - l) / 2;\n    if (check(mid))\n        r = mid;      // mid is feasible\n    else\n        l = mid + 1;  // need a larger answer\n}\nreturn l;",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "3. Binary Search on Answer\nint l = minPossible, r = maxPossible;\n\nwhile (l < r) {\n    int mid = l + (r - l) / 2;\n    if (check(mid))\n        r = mid;      // mid is feasible\n    else\n        l = mid + 1;  // need a larger answer\n}\nreturn l;",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "28-lRf_Abd_p6vPMcRwgO",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 180.3691900344129,
      "y": 3462.4446767171225,
      "width": 352.2997131347656,
      "height": 525,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0U",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2142356989,
      "version": 24,
      "versionNonce": 1519273401,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1783519612183,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Binary Search Recognition Keywords\n\nIf the problem mentions:\n\nMinimum possible\nMaximum possible\nSmallest X\nLargest X\nEarliest day\nLatest day\nMinimum capacity\nMaximum distance\nMinimum speed\nFirst occurrence\nLast occurrence\nSearch in sorted\nRotated array\nPeak\nFeasible\nCan we?\nAt least / At most",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Binary Search Recognition Keywords\n\nIf the problem mentions:\n\nMinimum possible\nMaximum possible\nSmallest X\nLargest X\nEarliest day\nLatest day\nMinimum capacity\nMaximum distance\nMinimum speed\nFirst occurrence\nLast occurrence\nSearch in sorted\nRotated array\nPeak\nFeasible\nCan we?\nAt least / At most",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "aVferfAJOHiBTz33zJaFd",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1448.7025233677464,
      "y": 2865.778010050456,
      "width": 626.0195922851564,
      "height": 400,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0X",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2042145075,
      "version": 27,
      "versionNonce": 279760471,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1783519612183,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Lower Bound (>= target)\n\n< target   < target   < target   >= target   >= target\nFalse      False      False       True        True\n                          ↑\n                    First True\n\nUpper Bound (> target)\n\n<= target   <= target   <= target   > target   > target\nFalse       False       False        True       True\n                             ↑\n                       First True\n\nThis \"find the first true\" perspective is the key insight \nthat extends beyond arrays to binary search on answers,",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Lower Bound (>= target)\n\n< target   < target   < target   >= target   >= target\nFalse      False      False       True        True\n                          ↑\n                    First True\n\nUpper Bound (> target)\n\n<= target   <= target   <= target   > target   > target\nFalse       False       False        True       True\n                             ↑\n                       First True\n\nThis \"find the first true\" perspective is the key insight \nthat extends beyond arrays to binary search on answers,",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "S6QCygEKkz3-cul8PN1ZO",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -394.6308099655871,
      "y": 4111.778010050455,
      "width": 1536.95947265625,
      "height": 200,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0a",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1581813235,
      "version": 232,
      "versionNonce": 940517017,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1783519612183,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "| Problem Type                              | Loop               | Mid Calculation | Left Update                      | Right Update                 | Return                |\n| ------------------------------------         | --------------      | ---------------    | ------------------------------      | ----------------------------     | ------------------      |\n| Exact Search                              | `start <= end`  | `(l+r)/2`       | `start = mid + 1`                | `end = mid - 1`                | Found index / `-1` |\n| Lower Bound                               | `start < end`  | `(l+r)/2`        | `start = mid + 1`                | `end = mid`                    | `start`            |\n| Upper Bound                               | `start < end`  | `(l+r)/2`        | `start = mid + 1`                | `end = mid`                    | `start`            |\n| First True (Binary Search on Answer) | `start < end`  | `(l+r)/2`        | `start = mid + 1` *(if false)* | `end = mid` *(if true)*       | `start`            |\n| Last True / Maximum Valid              | `start < end`    | `(l+r+1)/2`      | `start = mid` *(if true)*       | `end = mid - 1` *(if false)* | `start`            |\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "| Problem Type                              | Loop               | Mid Calculation | Left Update                      | Right Update                 | Return                |\n| ------------------------------------         | --------------      | ---------------    | ------------------------------      | ----------------------------     | ------------------      |\n| Exact Search                              | `start <= end`  | `(l+r)/2`       | `start = mid + 1`                | `end = mid - 1`                | Found index / `-1` |\n| Lower Bound                               | `start < end`  | `(l+r)/2`        | `start = mid + 1`                | `end = mid`                    | `start`            |\n| Upper Bound                               | `start < end`  | `(l+r)/2`        | `start = mid + 1`                | `end = mid`                    | `start`            |\n| First True (Binary Search on Answer) | `start < end`  | `(l+r)/2`        | `start = mid + 1` *(if false)* | `end = mid` *(if true)*       | `start`            |\n| Last True / Maximum Valid              | `start < end`    | `(l+r+1)/2`      | `start = mid` *(if true)*       | `end = mid - 1` *(if false)* | `start`            |\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
