      "text": "Functional Requirements\n1) Get tinyUrl \n2) Redirect to main URL using tinyUrl\n\n\nNon-Functional Requirements\n1) Consistence URL store\n2) Available for redirect\n3) scalable to handle 10M request/second",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Functional Requirements\n1) Get tinyUrl \n2) Redirect to main URL using tinyUrl\n\n\nNon-Functional Requirements\n1) Consistence URL store\n2) Available for redirect\n3) scalable to handle 10M request/second",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
