    {
      "id": "fWszz8pqX7wH9SoVvyTSm",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1010.6071980794281,
      "y": 4895.004185994462,
      "width": 623.8595581054688,
      "height": 225,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1H",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 12980825,
      "version": 392,
      "versionNonce": 998209849,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783521344845,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Pros\n1) Muliple tinyUrl Service (scalable)\n2) No single point of failure service side\n3) Individual DB for replica and master so reduse overhead\nof read and write on single DB.\n4) Sequence gen is unique which can be use to generate tinyURL\n\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Pros\n1) Muliple tinyUrl Service (scalable)\n2) No single point of failure service side\n3) Individual DB for replica and master so reduse overhead\nof read and write on single DB.\n4) Sequence gen is unique which can be use to generate tinyURL\n\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "EfjDxDVu3ofmMm4VvBS7r",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1010.6071980794281,
      "y": 5503.575614565891,
      "width": 636.5794677734375,
      "height": 275,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1HV",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 925124825,
      "version": 907,
      "versionNonce": 1771826135,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783521780448,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Pros\n1) Scalable\n2) Redis global count which is central of each random geneator\n3) Reduce latency as Redis is in memory with locking to be sure\nno same number will be return to RG.\n4) Store global counter value in DB using fixed interval so have \nbackup when it will start again.\n4) Less db call only for storing url.\n5) Store fixed tiny url and orignal URL in CDN for faster access.\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Pros\n1) Scalable\n2) Redis global count which is central of each random geneator\n3) Reduce latency as Redis is in memory with locking to be sure\nno same number will be return to RG.\n4) Store global counter value in DB using fixed interval so have \nbackup when it will start again.\n4) Less db call only for storing url.\n5) Store fixed tiny url and orignal URL in CDN for faster access.\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
