    {
      "id": "CDBA4tqO2P2Qd_LbcKz-1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1014.8929123651424,
      "y": 5142.147043137319,
      "width": 623.819580078125,
      "height": 250,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1O",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1251071481,
      "version": 529,
      "versionNonce": 972405623,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783521484044,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "cons\n1) Still takes time to redirect (latency as read from db which\nis IO operation)\n2) low throughput as request need to traves from multiple\nservice to db to main url.\n3) TinyUrl need to be consitent but predictable as we are using\ngenerate sequence feature of db.\n4) Sequence has limitation. No good for million request.\n(ex 10M request for new tinyUrl db got stuck)\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "cons\n1) Still takes time to redirect (latency as read from db which\nis IO operation)\n2) low throughput as request need to traves from multiple\nservice to db to main url.\n3) TinyUrl need to be consitent but predictable as we are using\ngenerate sequence feature of db.\n4) Sequence has limitation. No good for million request.\n(ex 10M request for new tinyUrl db got stuck)\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "LzFGi3U22lBiTW6JtQDWx",
